TwistieNav Plugin for Bootstrap 3 template

Adds drop-down navigation menus to breadcrumbs (and eventually "pageId" element)

All documentation for this plugin can be found at
http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugin:twistienav4bootstrap3

If you install this plugin manually, make sure it is installed in
lib/plugins/twistienav4bootstrap3/ - if the folder name is different it
will not work!

Please refer to http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugins for additional info
on how to install plugins in DokuWiki.

